# Union operator set for all shipped fono voice models (onnxruntime 1.24.2).
# Merged union of every previously-generated config (mirror + fono) so the
# minimal runtime can load EVERY shipped model: Piper voices (incl. LSTM /
# MatMulInteger variants) AND Kokoro q8f16 (needs Greater(13), If). Regenerate
# with scripts/merge-ort-configs.py over the per-set configs, or from the full
# model set via create_reduced_build_config.py --format ORT --enable_type_reduction.
